OL,6,FThousands of teachers from across
OL,7,FEngland are warning that vaping in
OL,8,Fschools is causing widespread issues
OL,9,Fwith children's behaviour and health.
OL,11,FTeaching union NASUWT commissioned a
OL,12,Fsurvey of 4,000 teachers - and more
OL,13,Fthan 85% of them warned vaping on
OL,14,Fschool premises is causing problems.
OL,16,FIt comes as a Bath Professor who
OL,17,Ftested vapes in 30 schools in England
OL,18,Ffound Spice and THC present in vapes
OL,19,Fin 25 of those schools.
