OL,6,FHe is now fearful a child will die
OL,7,Fthis summer holiday because their vape
OL,8,Fis unknowingly laced with Spice.
OL,10,FAcross the country, teachers raised
OL,11,Ftheir concerns about the impact it was
OL,12,Fhaving on their education and the
OL,13,Fconcerning behaviour they were seeing
OL,14,Fattached to the habit.
OL,16,FNASUWT has shared data from the South
OL,17,FWest exclusively with ITV West
OL,18,FCountry. Almost 84% of those surveyed
OL,19,Fin the South West said vaping is an
OL,20,Fissue in their school.
