OL,6,FTeachers also spoke of it being
OL,7,Fcommonplace for students to miss
OL,8,Flessons so they can go to the toilet
OL,9,Fto vape, with some pupils lying that
OL,10,Fthey feel sick to get out of class.
OL,12,FIn their comments, teachers spoke of
OL,13,F"pressure" on students to buy and sell
OL,14,Fvapes - saying pupils were purchasing
OL,15,Fthem from "dealers" and likening this
OL,16,Fto county lines drug dealing.
