OL,6,FCounty lines operations are when drug
OL,7,Fdealers in major cities establish
OL,8,Fnetworks for the supply and sale of
OL,9,Fdrugs to users in towns and rural
OL,10,Fareas, using other people.
OL,12,FSome teaching staff also reported
OL,13,Fhaving to confiscate vapes from
OL,14,Fchildren as young as five.
OL,16,FVaping in lessons was described as a
OL,17,F"huge problem" by many of the teachers
OL,18,Fsurveyed, with them also warning
OL,19,Fpupils were regularly vaping on school
OL,20,Fbuses, at bus stops and in corridors.
