OL,6,FThey said vaping is so common in
OL,7,Ftoilets - where teachers cannot police
OL,8,Fit - that students who do not vape no
OL,9,Flonger want to use the bathrooms.
OL,11,FIt has also been blamed for damage to
OL,12,Fschool property as students try to get
OL,13,Frid of used vapes by stuffing them
OL,14,Finto sinks and pipes.
OL,16,FTeachers say they are also having to
OL,17,Fspend more time policing vape use -
OL,18,Fincluding searching school bags on
OL,19,Ftrips.
