OL,6,FOne teacher said they found children
OL,7,Fin Year 1 and Year 2 with vapes - they
OL,8,Fwere five and six years old.
OL,10,F"The vapes were given to the children
OL,11,Fby their mum and Friday is their
OL,12,F'smoking day'," they added.
OL,14,FAnother spoke of catching students
OL,15,Fwith vapes containing THC, describing
OL,16,Fthem as "highly dangerous" and having
OL,17,Fan impact on their education.
