OL,6,F"Parents don't seem to care," one
OL,7,Fteacher wrote. "Some actually buy the
OL,8,Fvapes for the kids. The government
OL,9,Fneed to really make this a priority.
OL,10,FThis is going to be the next public
OL,11,Fhealth crisis."
OL,13,FDr Patrick Roach, General Secretary of
OL,14,FNASUWT, said: "More than eight in ten
OL,15,Fteachers have told us that vaping is a
OL,16,Fproblem in their schools.
