OL,6,F"We want to see the new Government act
OL,7,Fto protect children and young people
OL,8,Ffrom the dangers of vaping and we
OL,9,Fwelcome the proposed Tobacco and Vapes
OL,10,FBill.
OL,12,F"Vaping amongst young people has
OL,13,Fbecome a public health emergency.
OL,15,F"These products are highly accessible,
OL,16,Faffordable and marketed in ways which
OL,17,Fmake then attractive and appealing to
OL,18,Fchildren.
